# iverilog 编译&安装
```
sudo apt-get install gperf bison
sh autoconf.sh
git clone https://github.com/steveicarus/iverilog.git 
./configure --prefix=$PWD/../run/
make
make install
```
iverilog版本:ed7734c795b9879d3b541d18cf0e1725080649da

## 最简单例子
. ./env.sh
iverilog -o helloworld test/helloworld.v
vvp helloworld


